{"tid":1165070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"昨稱到找換店期間遭劫過百萬　警方揭屬自編自導拘8人","createTime":"2019-05-21T14:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T15:50:09.000Z","uid":47352,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6e31986cb20890eaf964a10aa7b48d3e0273feef","tid":1165070,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T14:17:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1458662-20190521.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1458662-20190521.htm&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TWVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=ed62e243\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1458662-20190521.htm&h=789701b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1458662-20190521.htm</a>2019-05-21 HKT 21:37<br />\n 分享工具  facebook  twitter<br />\n警方以涉嫌誤導警務人員、串謀行劫及非法禁錮，拘捕8名男子，指他們涉及昨日九龍城一宗懷疑自編自導自演的行劫案，其後因為分贓不均發生內訌，導致一名男子報稱在葵涌被非法禁錮的案件。<br />\n<br />\n九龍城警區總督察呂思灝說，案中大部分人無業，亦有人從事貿易及運輸生意，他們會被通宵扣查，會循涉案者的財務狀況、欠債紀錄及會否監守自盜等方向調查，不排除有進一步的拘捕行動，交由九龍城警區重案組接手調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，一名男子昨日報案指，到找換店期間被行劫，遭搶去178萬元，警方懷疑是有人自編自導自演劫案，安排同黨打劫自己，再設局中局，並無放入宣稱的178萬元現金在被搶劫的公事包中。而賊人由於分贓不均而內訌，禁錮其中一名策劃人。"},{"pid":"0debb797354f6cf868ee6a055eb456b651edbee9","tid":1165070,"uid":36253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T14:38:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b54107f447dccb0b9b176fde1809d7fbaacdd1","tid":1165070,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:13:08.000Z","msg":"成班貪錢傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3daae12798b823c989f5b6f12c2a87575eb02f","tid":1165070,"uid":142067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}